<data name="infoReadMe.Text" xml:space="preserve">

<value>Quick Help:

SETTINGS

Set your resolution over on the right.

For right now, you need to check 'Skip Recycle Bin.'

ADDONS

These are compatible skins available from LotroInterface.

Install whatever you find interesting.

They will show up on the Skins tab as selectable options.

SKINS

First enter a name.

Then choose from the grid one option per row.

The Turbine defaults are shown as "--"

Click Build.

In the game, go to UI settings, and select your new skin.

Exit the game and restart it.</value>
